init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As the story begins, a young man named Watashi is living a boring life in the provincial town of Kunimi.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One day, a mysterious girl named Himari appears in his monotonous life and offers him an opportunity to change.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari tells Watashi that she has the power to give him anything he desires.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari teases Watashi and tells him if he will believe her, she will give a demonstration of her magical powers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari tells Watashi that she will give him the ability to be able to use magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari warns him that he must not tell anyone about their agreement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari tells him that if he must have magic in his life, then he must make a deal with her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But he is desperate for magic in his life and agrees to the deal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari gives Watashi a book and tells him that he must pledge his spirit to her if he wants the power of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Watashi is elated about his new powers and begins to practice how he can use the magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Watashi chants the spell and a large sum of money materializes on the kitchen table.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Watashi is then shocked and confused on how he can be in such a place.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Himari appears in his home and tells him that he will never return to the world of the living.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is now trapped in the world of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He now has the ability of magic and because of his greediness for power, he will never be able to return back to his world.
